description: Blue-green moss creeps along the upper walls of the structure, which is leaning very slightly to one side.  Where windows once looked out, boards now cover the spaces, and dust, mud, and cobwebs sweep across amlost every surface.  The only clean space is a makeshift teller's cage and a polished silver sign set up in one corner.
